{"tid":1541784,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"對外文宣：出師有名！政府撤回=運動冇錯","createTime":"2019-09-04T16:03:42.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-11T06:56:43.000Z","uid":236799,"like":51,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"6efcc48529cbf57bc98b704c1894c47a46d55031","tid":1541784,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:03:42.000Z","msg":"林鄭宣佈撤回修例。呢一步, 就係<strong>承認</strong>運動至今係<strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">合理</span></strong>追求! <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府認錯而肯撤回, 表示運動本身唔係恐怖主義，示威者亦沒有參與暴動,<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">因為政府不會向恐怖份子妥協!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">而政府之首選擇了正面回應!</span></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n警察只係工具, 被政府用以掩飾錯誤。<br />\n警方至今所有行動: 鎮壓、濫捕、酷刑, etc.,<br />\n都係借執法之名, 實排除政治敵人,<br />\n並非警方口中的維持治安。<br />\n林鄭撤回, 就正正證明咗呢啲事實。<br />\n林鄭撤回,  就說明咗運動嘅訴求有其<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">正確性, 係做對事</span></span>!<br />\n<br />\n連政府都帶頭承認運動訴求, <span style=\"color: limegreen;\">警方更加冇權冇理據指控示威者做錯!</span><br />\n更莫論一眾撐警/藍絲的一切言論, 都係無理指控, 無名無實。<br />\n連政府都支持示威者, <span style=\"color: red;\">藍絲繼續糾纏下去則只會淪為一群反政府的反賊!</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n政府一句撤回, <br />\n就係對示威民眾講的一句<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">「你地冇做錯到!」</span></strong></span><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n五大訴求，缺一不可！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a220c6342943842f2064c6aeb38349cf4c8777a8","tid":1541784,"uid":117906,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:04:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">撤LLM 對準政權</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3E7OjKb.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3E7OjKb.gif&h=66b4ea40&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zNutjAi.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzNutjAi.jpg&h=1817afe5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">得到黨媒認證</span></strong></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sELTeyX.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsELTeyX.png&h=0e8c0efe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">#Chinazi旗係一個符號，不斷向世界輸出反共思想！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">#Chinazi 赤納粹</span></span></strong><br />\nChinazi就係China+Nazi。<br />\n赤=共產紅色恐怖, 納粹不解釋。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\"> 全民反共 對準政權！</span></span></strong><br />\n黑警、黨鐵，港共全部都係人民既敵人<br />\n而背後一直有一個終極大Boss中共<br />\n<br />\n呢一刻中共絕對係十個煲得兩個蓋，準備爆煲。<br />\n今日唔號召世界圍堵中共，更待何時？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: orange;\">用#Chinazi黎connect全世界</span></span></strong><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">1. Connect所有黃絲。</span></strong><br />\n殘酷既現實係，並唔係所有黃絲都支持勇武。但黃絲最驚就係共產黨打到黎，一於用反共connect呢班淺黃!<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">2. Connect部分中立/藍絲。</span></strong><br />\n中立/藍絲既上一輩，全部都係親身經歷過六四既年代，唔少甚至係大陸生活過。係大陸生活上所面對既不公義、中共點砌人生豬肉、佢地可能比我地感受更深。佢地唔會否認對共產黨既恐懼！一齊黎喚醒佢地對中共既不信任！<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">3. Connect全世界</span></strong><br />\nNazi既惡行到今時今日都依然係全世界既傷口，但佢地未必注意到係21世紀有個同Nazi不遑多讓既Chinazi！用#chinazi旗加海量文宣，話比佢地知我地既共同敵人係中共！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>目標：全香港市民都知到呢個符號！<br />\n請大家用各種創意方法令大家知道呢道Chinazi旗！<br />\n記住！存在即勝利！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: orange;\">雙手奉上</span></strong><br />\n<img src=\"https://upload.cc/i1/2019/09/02/9dojRG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fupload.cc%2Fi1%2F2019%2F09%2F02%2F9dojRG.png&h=baf47345&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/JXMrzU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FJXMrzU3.jpg&h=4fd76574&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/uZFWW8o.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FuZFWW8o.jpg&h=4196affc&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2c38728951882b5c27699fa80b3110b6baa53b62","tid":1541784,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:05:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7235056841ef08e38b379952ed3f74fcddce386d","tid":1541784,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:06:09.000Z","msg":"自推十連為敬<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"61a5a6b5e1f00cc80b53b4da985b35c3ba6cfa9d","tid":1541784,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:06:40.000Z","msg":"1/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"23690bb2256a93baa01fdd62012b059eeade33b6","tid":1541784,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:07:44.000Z","msg":"2/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0b4f39b5efcc9bd8359f2b09da1be93c7f9f99a","tid":1541784,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-04T16:08:55.000Z","msg":"3/10<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6062c33e31a9083d25a570aa2938946b5fe8d25","tid":1541784,"uid":236799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy